{"tid":1068621,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"Metal detecting 尋寶","createTime":"2019-03-19T10:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T15:23:57.000Z","uid":89939,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb13b7fa7ce23b973121ad57c400225324ab377","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:56:10.000Z","msg":"買部手持金屬探測器去沙灘揾銀仔或者上山搵二戰物品都得, 當尋寶咁玩 <br />\n<br />\n我可以推薦一啲入門gear, 入門探測器大約二千之內都好多選擇, 想搵人組團一齊去掃沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港都有一隊外國人組成既探測隊, 專門上山揾二戰物品<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-THAvd1ItM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db-THAvd1ItM&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=ada7e687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-THAvd1ItM</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地甚至係畢架山搵到1947年墜機遺失既墨西哥金幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一個值2000美金:<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/660x385/public/images/methode/2017/02/03/87df0b6a-e217-11e6-8801-9f557f980a64_660x385.JPG?itok=NSN15t7Z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F660x385%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F87df0b6a-e217-11e6-8801-9f557f980a64_660x385.JPG%3Fitok%3DNSN15t7Z&h=d984a503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際係點(香港多數得外國人玩):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OsoFJdLhlAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOsoFJdLhlAQ&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=32f33ca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OsoFJdLhlAQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vfFcu91_-o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4vfFcu91_-o&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=713dbc8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vfFcu91_-o</a><br />\n<br />\n之前沙灘自己一個掃既成果:<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fdZPwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfdZPwx.jpg&h=d3889883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人有興趣既tg @appera 夠人會開telegram group傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2dca7b0894e0e26df3a29ad3c40d92e83ad97b","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8ce531ad30bd4961915e7eb581ad74e75b3a0f","tid":1068621,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"想要架車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb9ff696629df1c0bb12c15dd71a57899fe0f4e","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecae9ccbcfd098982df70dbf4eec846443c42ed3","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369a5750bfa6606227f912d757353184a804f7c9","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35e1560a0f891751924d277b8c4fc454a206517","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b42ab99c934e246c9be06a34096b0db30e57d8","tid":1068621,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T18:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/l